# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# FOODSbyme Website — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in the values.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Partnership application form endpoint
# Without this, form submissions fall back to opening the visitor's email client
# (mailto:partnerships@foodsbyme.com), which requires their email app to be set up.
#
# To use Formspree (recommended — free tier available):
#   1. Go to https://formspree.io and create a free account
#   2. Create a new form and set the notification email to partnerships@foodsbyme.com
#   3. Copy the form endpoint URL (e.g. https://formspree.io/f/abcdefgh)
#   4. Paste it below and set this variable in your hosting environment (e.g. Vercel)
#
NEXT_PUBLIC_FLEET_ENDPOINT=
